{"tid":681852,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家地鐵成日開啲開車出嚟係做乜","createTime":"2018-05-28T11:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T11:40:07.000Z","uid":133528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"745e30a9fab851904d0e201afa6a0d8698394b66","tid":681852,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"小弟係觀塘返工放工，有時放工繁忙時間又熱又多人，等左好耐終於有一班車嚟緊，然後就聽到廣播話本班列車將不會接載乘客。你話如果班車係由調景嶺開去繁忙嘅地鐵站，直接去某啲地鐵站疏導人流，咁觀塘應該係第一個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話如果係藍田油塘嗰啲站，冇乜人我都可以理解，但觀塘牛頭角呢啲真係諗唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，正常打工仔，平日返工冇理由揸車，巴士同的士又會塞車，求理性分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f0a0d63b1f3b882a608ce5ce781040f05dc390","tid":681852,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗鐵"},{"pid":"d2b0f4eeb684c8330b9fc8287883be0ce209e330","tid":681852,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"其實係收車返廠<br />\n<br />\n純9 up"}]}